{"id": "1430827301339402281", "channel_id": "1430827301339402281", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：图鲁EP·幼王的孤途 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜OST：图鲁EP·幼王的孤途**\n他以王冠加诸己身，他以镣铐加诸己身。\n那是短暂虚幻的暖意，那是注定覆灭的往日荣光。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"Tulu EP· Young King's Lonely Journey\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: Tulu EP· Young King's Lonely Journey**\nHe crowned himself with the crown; he shackled himself with the throne.\nThat was a brief and illusory warmth; that was the past glory destined to be undone.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-10-23T07:56:52.125000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "T_sleepy", "emoji_id": "1400771754573692928", "count": 11}, {"emoji": "love", "emoji_id": "1356053099931897977", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "T_sleep2", "emoji_id": "1356085993626665200", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "💕", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1430827301767086121", "filename": "OST-250827.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1807603, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1430827301339402281/1430827301767086121/OST-250827.jpg?ex=69cccfc4&is=69cb7e44&hm=5daf298359e19fe811f72ff64219bd3c1277700a1baf0b50ade3fb11f0b2a504&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430827301339402281", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：图鲁EP·幼王的孤途", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033"}
{"id": "1430827931399098401", "channel_id": "1430827301339402281", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02. 加冕-The Coronation-**\n\n幼王接受了这笔交易。\n他说，我的国将安然无恙。\n\nThe young king accepted the deal.\n\"My country shall be safe and sound,\" he said.", "timestamp": "2025-10-23T07:59:22.343000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1430827930812153938", "filename": "02._-The_Coronation-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 33410102, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1430827301339402281/1430827930812153938/02._-The_Coronation-.wav?ex=69ccd05a&is=69cb7eda&hm=4b452bac6f1131197164468cec4b9fdd574e6237d8d0b6ab7558b8e9a290847e&"}, {"id": "1430827931378257950", "filename": "2_.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1216801, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1430827301339402281/1430827931378257950/2_.jpg?ex=69ccd05a&is=69cb7eda&hm=c745158e3564cbebb4a7a42adc28af20be3d9767e62b4198b969e40a0f8e9453&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430827301339402281", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：图鲁EP·幼王的孤途", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033"}
{"id": "1430827938584068158", "channel_id": "1430827301339402281", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.  余将独行-I Shall Walk Alone-**\n\n后来者会在沉重的馈赠下，找到这么一行脚注。\n唯一逃避当英雄的人成为了英雄，珍视朋友的孩子只剩下唯一的朋友。\n\nFuture arrivals, under the weight of the heavy bestowment, will find this footnote:\nHe who fled the hero's crown, became the hero; he who cherished his friends, lost all but one.", "timestamp": "2025-10-23T07:59:24.056000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1430827937954795582", "filename": "1_.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1239142, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1430827301339402281/1430827937954795582/1_.jpg?ex=69ccd05b&is=69cb7edb&hm=cc5972cfa6629479414f0ec2ae98a80f38d5ad209b09c80eb46b2dd0c265a020&"}, {"id": "1430827938278019104", "filename": "01._-I_Shall_Walk_Alone-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 44498246, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1430827301339402281/1430827938278019104/01._-I_Shall_Walk_Alone-.wav?ex=69ccd05b&is=69cb7edb&hm=17389a1f4d0cc8ba73c17e5dbe4c3e99c921182a7160aa85997b9169ceab3337&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430827301339402281", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：图鲁EP·幼王的孤途", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033"}
{"id": "1430828021354463325", "channel_id": "1430827301339402281", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03. 无边苦寂的王土-Boundless Land of Sorrow-**\n\n少年为短暂的一切，付出了被索偿的代价。\n如今，只剩静默的权柄与他相伴。\n王要睡去了，他在梦中迎来世界的尽头。\n\nThe youth paid the price demanded for all that was fleeting.\nNow, only the silent scepter keeps him company.\nThe young king shall fall asleep, and in his dreams, he shall meet the end of the world.", "timestamp": "2025-10-23T07:59:43.790000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1430828020754546709", "filename": "3_.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1247180, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1430827301339402281/1430828020754546709/3_.jpg?ex=69ccd06f&is=69cb7eef&hm=00f81a69422f894e3facdf7fe17a96de5a9fc737fa5983b80f56559311e61f90&"}, {"id": "1430828021039763556", "filename": "03.-Boundless_Land_of_Sorrow-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 42652210, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1430827301339402281/1430828021039763556/03.-Boundless_Land_of_Sorrow-.wav?ex=69ccd06f&is=69cb7eef&hm=8d84a34b744177bf72445004c6843e6b7a53e0a0939c52f8cf39a9b129722857&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1430827301339402281", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：图鲁EP·幼王的孤途", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033"}
